      "content": "that seems kinda a harsh take lol. like, dont you think there's a massive difference between the UN failing to stop a war and the UN actually having no legitimacy at all? i feel like some people argue the whole system is just fundamentally broken and outdated regardless of what happens in specific conflicts.",
